{"id":1883,"date":"2020-08-14T17:14:50","date_gmt":"2020-08-14T10:14:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?page_id=1883"},"modified":"2024-04-17T15:05:31","modified_gmt":"2024-04-17T08:05:31","slug":"green-policy-vi","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/green-policy-vi\/","title":{"rendered":"Ch\u00ednh S\u00e1ch Xanh"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47eu0ati fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Header-Going-Green-Caravelle.jpg 1360w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d9bbc0ffc3b6597b323500d87ecabcb9_Header-Going-Green-Caravelle-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Header-Going-Green-Caravelle.jpg\" alt=\"Header-Going-Green-Caravelle\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-48g02qao fg-section fg-text-dark\" id=\"intro\"><div class=\"fg-container container-fluid fg-container-fluid fg-container-lvl--1 fg-container-no-padding\"><div class=\"fg-row row fg-row-no-gutter   \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-48g02qap fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h5 class=\"ffb-id-48g02qas fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\">CH&Iacute;NH S&Aacute;CH PH&Aacute;T TRI\u1ec2N B\u1ec0N V\u1eeeNG<\/h3>\n<p><\/h5><div class=\"ffb-id-48g02qat fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c n&acirc;ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 th&acirc;n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111&oacute;ng g&oacute;p cho c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, Caravelle Saigon cam k\u1ebft th&acirc;n ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng th&acirc;n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, t\u1eeb \u0111&oacute; li&ecirc;n t\u1ee5c ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n v&agrave; tu&acirc;n th\u1ee7 ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng v\u1ec1 M&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, N\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v&agrave; X&atilde; h\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">V\u1edbi t\u1ea7m nh&igrave;n tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p ra Nh&agrave; Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1 v&agrave; ch\u1ec9 c&aacute;ch c&aacute;c di s\u1ea3n v\u0103n h&oacute;a, trung t&acirc;m mua s\u1eafm v&agrave;i ph&uacute;t \u0111i b\u1ed9, Caravelle Saigon vinh d\u1ef1 l&agrave; bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh, ki&ecirc;u h&atilde;nh \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng qua nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. Caravelle Saigon cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 l\u01b0u tr&uacute; 5 sao v\u1edbi 333 ph&ograve;ng sang tr\u1ecdng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, c&ugrave;ng v\u1edbi c&aacute;c ph&ograve;ng ti\u1ec7c \u0111a ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng, h\u1ed3 b\u01a1i, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gym &amp; spa, nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng v&agrave; qu&aacute;n bar.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">T\u1ea1i Caravelle, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i \u01b0u ti&ecirc;n v&agrave; \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i l&agrave;m vi\u1ec7c an to&agrave;n, th&acirc;n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho c&aacute;c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khuy\u1ebfn kh&iacute;ch c&aacute;c s&aacute;ng ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200bxanh nh\u1eb1m gi\u1ea3m nh\u1eb9 t&aacute;c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. V\u1edbi s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh n&agrave;y, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i \u0111&atilde; thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp, tri\u1ec3n khai v&agrave; duy tr&igrave; H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l&yacute; m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v&agrave; H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l&yacute; n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng theo ti&ecirc;u chu\u1ea9n EarthCheck.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">CARAVELLE SAIGON CAM K\u1ebeT:<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Tr&aacute;nh t&aacute;c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti&ecirc;u c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v&agrave; t\u1ed1i \u0111a h&oacute;a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">C\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn li&ecirc;n t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a c&aacute;c s&aacute;ng ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200bxanh<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Tu&acirc;n th\u1ee7 c&aacute;c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ch&iacute;nh ph\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 kh&iacute;a c\u1ea1nh m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v&agrave; thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111&aacute;nh gi&aacute; h&agrave;ng n\u0103m v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe &amp; an to&agrave;n t\u1ea1i n\u01a1i l&agrave;m vi\u1ec7c theo ti&ecirc;u chu\u1ea9n Earthcheck.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">T\u1eadp trung tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng lao \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u01afu ti&ecirc;n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c&aacute;c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v&agrave; tu&acirc;n th\u1ee7 c&aacute;c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 giao d\u1ecbch c&ocirc;ng b\u1eb1ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">N&acirc;ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 v\u1ec1 t&iacute;nh b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng &amp; x&atilde; h\u1ed9i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">-------------<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Caravelle Saigon \u0111&aacute;nh gi&aacute; cao v&agrave; khuy\u1ebfn kh&iacute;ch nh\u1eefng s&aacute;ng ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200bxanh t\u1eeb c&aacute;c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1, kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t&aacute;c v&agrave; c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng; trong \u0111&oacute; s\u1ebd l&agrave; \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ec3 Caravelle S&agrave;i G&ograve;n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n c&aacute;c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng v\u1ec1 m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v&agrave; x&atilde; h\u1ed9i. H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn n&agrave;y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt h&agrave;ng n\u0103m.<\/p>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 734px;top: 636.866px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-48g02qao{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;} .ffb-id-48g02qap{ text-align: center;}.ffb-id-48g02qat ,.ffb-id-48g02qat:before,.ffb-id-48g02qat:after,.ffb-id-48g02qat *,.ffb-id-48g02qat *:before,.ffb-id-48g02qat *:after{ color: #797979 !important;}.ffb-id-48g02qat{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-48g02qat:before,.ffb-id-48g02qat:after,.ffb-id-48g02qat:hover,.ffb-id-48g02qat:focus,.ffb-id-48g02qat *,.ffb-id-48g02qat *:before,.ffb-id-48g02qat *:after,.ffb-id-48g02qat *:hover,.ffb-id-48g02qat *:focus{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-48g02qat{ font-size: 13px !important;}.ffb-id-48g02qat ,.ffb-id-48g02qat:before,.ffb-id-48g02qat:after,.ffb-id-48g02qat:hover,.ffb-id-48g02qat:focus,.ffb-id-48g02qat *,.ffb-id-48g02qat *:before,.ffb-id-48g02qat *:after,.ffb-id-48g02qat *:hove